{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"1":{"eng-name":"Purification (Kitab Al-Taharah)","ara-name":"كتاب الطهارة"}},"section_detail":{"1":{"hadithnumber_first":1,"hadithnumber_last":390,"arabicnumber_first":1,"arabicnumber_last":390}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":196,"arabicnumber":196,"text":"حَدَّثَنَا قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ، حَدَّثَنَا اللَّيْثُ، عَنْ عَقِيلٍ، عَنِ الزُّهْرِيِّ، عَنْ عُبَيْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ، عَنِ ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ، أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ صلى الله عليه وسلم شَرِبَ لَبَنًا فَدَعَا بِمَاءٍ فَتَمَضْمَضَ ثُمَّ قَالَ ‏ \"‏ إِنَّ لَهُ دَسَمًا ‏\"‏ ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (211) Sahih Muslim (358)"}],"reference":{"book":1,"hadith":196},"chapter":{"id":77,"ara-name":"باب فِي الْوُضُوءِ مِنَ اللَّبَنِ","eng-name":"Wudu' From (Drinking) Milk","isFirstHadith":true}}]}